<item>
            <title>[SOLR-1577] undesirable dataDir default in example config</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-1577</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;dataDir in the example solrconfig.xml defaults to ./solr/data (as opposed to the solr home)&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://search.lucidimagination.com/search/document/7759f05f576d6727&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://search.lucidimagination.com/search/document/7759f05f576d6727&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://search.lucidimagination.com/search/document/c5ae6fa490d0f59a&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://search.lucidimagination.com/search/document/c5ae6fa490d0f59a&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
